de.rincewind.api.gui.elements

Class ElementSwitcher.SwitchItem<S>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rincewind.api.gui.elements.ElementSwitcher.SwitchItem<S>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - specifying value type. It is automaticly the same, you set in the root class ElementSwitcher as the parameter T.
    Enclosing interface:
    ElementSwitcher<T>

    public static class ElementSwitcher.SwitchItem<S>
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the class, you can add to the ElementSwitcher. You have to add an ItemStack / Icon, witch will be displayed, when this instance is matched, and a value with an specified type. The value is only for you something to save in each entry.

    2.3.3
